quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  97,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  97,1,hum ne is ( quran ) ko shab qader mein nazil ( karna shuru )kiya
  97,2,aur tumhekiya maloom ke shab qaderkiya hai ?
  97,3,shab qader hazaar mahinay se behtar hai
  97,4,is mein rooh ( al-ameen ) aur farishtay har kaam ke ( intizam ke ) liye apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se utartay hain
  97,5,yeh ( raat ) tulu subah taq ( Amaan aur ) salamti hai
